snippet.title: Block Royale In Game Footage
snippet.description: Welcome to the newest high-intensity, action-packed block puzzle game. Take to the battlefield for intense 4 person multiplayer battles with people from across the world.  Use exciting special abilities to attack other combatants or to defend your field, experience easy to use controls including automatic shape rotation. Hone your skills in single player vs 3 AI bots. Download now and battle for victory!
